               <msContents>
                  <summary>General Epistles, F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-16v: 1 Peter. F<locus target="#16v">16v, </locus>-18r: 2 Peter.  Several folios are missing between f<locus target="#12">12, </locus> and 13, including most of 1 John. 18rv: 2 John. F<locus target="#18v">18v, </locus>-19v: 3 John. F<locus target="#19v">19v, </locus>-25v: James: l18-e19th. F<locus target="#25v">25v, </locus>-27r: Jude. Ff. i rv: pen trials, including the copying of a section from 1 Peter. The manuscript has been foliated with stamped, blue numbers. <locus target="#27v">27v</locus>: alphebet exercises.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="27r" facs="002">Fols 1r–27r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3506CatholicEpis">Catholic
                                                  Epistles</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="1r" to="1v" facs="002">Fols 1r–1v, </locus>
                        <locus from="11r" to="16v" facs="012">11r–16v</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3507Epistle">First Epistle of
                                                  Peter</title>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="16v" facs="018">Fols 16v and following, </locus>
                        <locus from="2r" to="5v" facs="003">2r–5v</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3508Epistle">Second Epistle of
                                                  Peter</title>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="5v" to="10v" facs="007">Fols 5v–10v, </locus>
                        <locus from="17r" to="18r" facs="018">17r–18r</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3509Epistle">First Epistle of
                                                  John</title>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="18r" to="18v" facs="019">Fols 18r–18v</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3510Epistle">Second Epistle of
                                                  John</title>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <locus from="18v" to="19v" facs="020">Fols 18v–19v</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3511Epistle">Third Epistle of
                                                  John</title>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                        <locus from="19v" to="25v" facs="021">Fols 19v–25v</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3512Epistle">Epistle of
                                                  James</title>
                      </msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
